<p class="ayah 7-33" id="33" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَرَّمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(had) forbidden</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">my Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْفَوَٲحِشَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the shameful deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ظَهَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) apparent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَطَنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is concealed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْإِثْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the sin,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْبَغْىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the oppression</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first 