 class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَلَـٰمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Peace</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(be) upon you.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَدْخُلُوهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they have entered it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَطْمَعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">hope.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>46<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
