nText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wrongdoers.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>47<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
