<p class="ayah 7-51" id="51" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّخَذُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">took</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دِينَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their religion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهْوًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) an amusement</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَعِبًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and play</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَغَرَّتْهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and deluded them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَيَوٲةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the life</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلدُّنْيَا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the world.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱلْيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So today</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَنسَـٰهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We forget them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">as</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَسُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they forgot</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><sp