<p class="ayah 7-101" id="101" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تِلْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">These</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(were) the cities -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَقُصُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We relate</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنۢبَآئِهَا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their news.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَتْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُسُلُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their Messengers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with clear proofs,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span cla