<p class="ayah 7-103" id="103" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعَثْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We sent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنۢ بَعْدِهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّوسَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Musa</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Our Signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِرْعَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Firaun</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَلَإِيْهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and his chiefs,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَظَلَمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But they were unjust</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱنظُرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَيْفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">how</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top 