<p class="ayah 7-104" id="104" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ مُوسَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Musa said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰفِرْعَوْنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O Firaun!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, I am</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَسُولٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the worlds</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>104<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
