<p class="ayah 7-144" id="144" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰمُوسَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O Musa!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱصْطَفَيْتُكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have chosen you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّاسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِرِسَـٰلَـٰتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with My Messages</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبِكَلَـٰمِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and with My words.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَخُذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So take</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاتَيْتُكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I have given you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكُن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّـٰكِرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the grateful.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>144<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 7-145" id="145" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَتَبْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And We ordained (laws)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَلْوَاحِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the tablets -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّوْعِظَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an instruction</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتَفْصِيلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and explanation</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّكُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَخُذْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`So take them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِقُوَّةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with firmness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأْمُرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and order</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْمَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْخُذُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[to] take</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِأَحْسَنِهَا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) best of it.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَأُوْرِيكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I will show you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَارَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) home</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْفَـٰسِقِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the defiantly disobedient.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>145<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 7-146" id="146" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَأَصْرِفُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I will turn away</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَـٰتِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">My Signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَكَبَّرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">are arrogant</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِغَيْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">without</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَقِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] right;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">sign,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّا يُؤْمِنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will not believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) way</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرُّشْدِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the righteousness,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا يَتَّخِذُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will not take it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) a way,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) way</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْغَىِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) [the] error,</span></span><s