<p class="ayah 7-164" id="164" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a community</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Why</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعِظُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) you preach</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْمًا‌ۙ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a people,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(whom) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُهْلِكُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is going to) destroy them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُعَذِّبُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">punish them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(with) a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar 