<p class="ayah 7-165" id="165" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَسُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they forgot</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُكِّرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they had been reminded</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with [it],</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنجَيْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We saved</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنْهَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">forbade</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[from]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسُّوٓءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the evil,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَخَذْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and We seized</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top fi