<p class="ayah 7-181" id="181" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمِمَّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And of (those) whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقْنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a nation,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَهْدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who guides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحَقِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with the truth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and thereby</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْدِلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they establish justice.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>181<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
