<p class="ayah 7-185" id="185" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنظُرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they look</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَلَكُوتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) dominion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(every)thing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَسَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">perhaps</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top fir